const ai_answer_format_preferences = @md
- Use clear structure with #, ## and ### headings
- Prefer bullet points and numbered lists over long paragraphs
- Bold only key terms or important takeaways
- Keep paragraphs short and add blank lines between sections
- Use --- to separate major sections when needed
- Use tables only when they improve clarity; keep them simple and easy to scan
;;

